  <brief_title>Energy Load in Patients With Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome (ARDS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Energy Load During Mechanical Ventilation in Patients With Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome (ARDS)</official_title>
