  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigator would assess if there is an incremental energy load during mechanical
      ventilation in Acute Respiratory Distress Syndrome (ARDS) patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigator would study the inspiratory and expiratory pressure volume curve in ARDS
      patients and investigate if there is a correlation between the energy loss (hysteresis
      curve) and the severity of disease.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
